____________________________________________________________________________

And &quot;Somebody&quot;, and it's not my ISP, keeps on blocking my listening port and slows down my bandwidth all the time to an extreme low, but then I change it, and the speed picks up, then they find me, and.. on and on..
The only thing I can do, is to appeal to you who are Christians, to help me. Please seed these torrents with me, because I don't know how much longer I'm able to do this. Not for long, I fear. And I live in Norway, a so called &quot;free Nation&quot; of the western world.. And then I'm accused of being a &quot;conspiracy-theorist&quot;.. :-)

Anyway: A while ago I uploaded this movie by Jonathan Gray, and named it &quot;Lamb Of God And Ark Of The Covenant&quot;. It's now uploaded on the TorrentBox site as well.
Truly amazing stuff. And he has several more amazing DVDs to share with us. I've bought them, And his books too, and they blow my mind...

You can find them, and prescribe to his free newsletter at:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://beforeus.com/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://beforeus.com/&lt;/a&gt;

Upon prescription, you'll receive special offers not available to the general public.

What you are about to see in this movie may:
1: Leave you in awe and wonder, or you
2: may not believe in it, and subsequently
3: also fail to see it's significance.

I hope you are among those under point 1.
Mr Gray is NOT a wealthy man. In fact he has sold his house and rents a place to live, just so that he can travel in search for evidence of the Bible's accuracy. I've made a small upload Named: &quot;Surprising Discoveries Presented By Jonathan Gray&quot;, where he tells you a little about what he has to offer.

I make this upload in spite of Mr. Gray's financial situation, because this is so important and exceptional stuff, so I take that chance in the Name of Jesus. Just to get this footage out before it's too late.

This one is about the findings of the crossing point of Israel in the Red Sea. It'll blow your mind. I'll just Name it &quot;The Red Sea Crossing - The Sea Yields Proof - DivX&quot;

But please, after watching this: If you're really a Christian and have the opportunity, and want to support a brother who works full-time for Jesus, go to Mr Gray's website and preferably order at least a book or a DVD or something.

Greetings from Verifire.

